author: Play On Tabletop
description:
This one will be explosive just like the effects provided by episode sponsor Deadly Print Studios! https://deadlyprintstudio.com/

Imperial Knights and Adeptus Mechanicus have sent a Questor Forge Pack to hunt down some T'au and are met with resistance of the Mont'ka variety. Jind's bombastic energy powers the Imperial Knights with his favourite little Adeptus Mechanicus allies. T'au Nick brings some big guns against the Imperial's big bads.
